I don't think you've thought
through this, old friend.


254
00:13:08.366 --> 00:13:11.285
We've got a dynamic here.
I'm the hero.


255
00:13:11.327 --> 00:13:13.663
You're the guy who gets
to hang out with the hero.


256
00:13:13.705 --> 00:13:15.957
Now, with that
firmly reestablished,


257
00:13:15.998 --> 00:13:18.876
let's go get some churros.

258
00:13:20.753 --> 00:13:23.673
Sir, if you don't
recognize my contributions,


259
00:13:23.715 --> 00:13:27.719
