explore other opportunities.


260
00:13:27.760 --> 00:13:29.679
Hm. Okay.

261
00:13:29.721 --> 00:13:33.558
- Well, if you feel that
strongly about it... - Oh.


262
00:13:33.599 --> 00:13:35.143
Okay then. Uh...

263
00:13:35.184 --> 00:13:38.521
If you feel that strongly about
me feeling strongly about it--


264
00:13:38.563 --> 00:13:41.566
