Aren't you forgetting someone?


299
00:15:34.345 --> 00:15:36.264
The Master of Nightmares,

300
00:15:36.305 --> 00:15:37.932
the Duke of Darkness,

301
00:15:37.974 --> 00:15:41.185
the broken nightlight
