00:16:40.745 --> 00:16:42.497
Megamind left you in charge.

328
00:16:42.538 --> 00:16:43.831
Pierre Pressure:
I do!


329
00:16:43.873 --> 00:16:45.249
Ugh, seriously?!

330
00:16:45.291 --> 00:16:49.003
How many leaders think
we should pay Megamind a visit?


331
00:16:49.045 --> 00:16:50.505
Pierre:
I do!


332
00:16:50.546 --> 00:16:51.839
Fine. It's settled then.

333
00:16:51.881 --> 00:16:55.426
I agree. But, there is
just one little thing


334
00:16:55.468 --> 00:16:57.178
to take care of first.

335
