Guard:
Hey, Doomy Glooms! No scheming during lunch!


336
00:17:01.140 --> 00:17:03.976
This was a nice place
to lay low for a while,


337
00:17:04.018 --> 00:17:06.729
but we've got some
business to take care of.


338
00:17:06.771 --> 00:17:09.732
Nighty-Knight:
Hello darkness, my old friend.


339
00:17:11.818 --> 00:17:12.944
Ha!

340
00:17:13.194 --> 00:17:14.404
Whoa! Ah!

341
00:17:16.364 --> 00:17:18.241
I can't move!

342
