in an invisible box!


345
00:17:34.298 --> 00:17:35.925
Behemoth? Go gravel.

346
00:17:50.857 --> 00:17:52.817
Guard:
Oh, please don't hurt me!


347
00:17:52.859 --> 00:17:55.278
We'll show ourselves out.

348
00:18:01.200 --> 00:18:03.578
Megamind, here we come.

349
00:18:05.997 --> 00:18:09.042
Spokesman:
Ever feel like you're driving to the same job,


350
00:18:09.083 --> 00:18:10.376
drinking the same coffee,

351
00:18:10.418 --> 00:18:13.046
wearing the same outfit
almost every day?


352
00:18:13.087 --> 00:18:15.631
- Ugh. Yeah.
- Spokesman: Have you been wondering


353
00:18:15.673 --> 00:18:17.717
if there's more
you could be doing


354
00:18:17.759 --> 00:18:19.469
- to spice up your life?
- Yeah.


355
00:18:19.510 --> 00:18:21.012
Spokesman:
We have the answer.


356
00:18:21.054 --> 00:18:23.556
Have a Mr. Minion's Meat-sicle!

357
00:18:23.598 --> 00:18:25.725
Protein on the go!

358
00:18:25.767 --> 00:18:27.727
Okay, that really
under-delivered.


359
00:18:27.769 --> 00:18:29.270
Roxanne, I'm in great danger!

360
00:18:33.775 --> 00:18:35.777
How are you doing this?!

361
00:18:35.818 --> 00:18:38.738
Through the bobblehead of myself
I gave to you as a present.


362
00:18:38.780 --> 00:18:40.990
It's a tracking device
so I can look out for you.


363
00:18:41.032 --> 00:18:44.410
I'm flattered by this
invasion of my privacy.


364
00:18:44.452 --> 00:18:48.122
Come to the lair immediately.
My very life may depend on it!


365
00:18:48.706 --> 00:18:50.666
Hang on!
I'll be right there.


366
00:19:01.260 --> 00:19:02.387
Megamind?

367
00:19:02.887 --> 00:19:04.680
Megamind:
I'm in the kitchen! Hurry!


368
00:19:06.974 --> 00:19:10.686
- How dare you defy me, you--
