369
00:19:10.728 --> 00:19:12.563
I'll tell you what's happening!

370
00:19:12.605 --> 00:19:16.567
This disrespectful toaster
pastry refuses to toast!


371
00:19:16.609 --> 00:19:19.070
I thought this was
a matter of life and death!


372
00:19:19.112 --> 00:19:22.115
Newsflash! I need food,
or I'll starve.


373
00:19:22.156 --> 00:19:24.283
Besides, I couldn't
reach the pancakes.


374
00:19:25.701 --> 00:19:28.538
Newsflash!
Toasters need to be plugged in


375
00:19:28.579 --> 00:19:29.872
