376
00:19:29.914 --> 00:19:33.459
Show me what you did,
sorceress!


377
00:19:33.501 --> 00:19:36.713
Maybe you should call Chum?

378
00:19:36.754 --> 00:19:39.757
I'm fully capable of
taking care of myself.


379
00:19:39.799 --> 00:19:43.094
