387
00:20:02.029 --> 00:20:04.657
Is that any way to
welcome your old crew?


388
00:20:05.158 --> 00:20:08.786
I mean...
what an unpleasant surprise!


389
00:20:08.828 --> 00:20:11.247
My old evil supervillain team.

390
00:20:11.289 --> 00:20:14.292
Nighty-Knight:
You must be so stoked to see us.


391
00:20:14.333 --> 00:20:17.795
Stoked doesn't begin to
describe it, Fright Night.


392
00:20:17.837 --> 00:20:22.383
Get zis. He now wants
to be called "Nighty-Knight."


393
00:20:22.425 --> 00:20:23.676
Nighty-Knight:
It's scarier!


394
00:20:23.718 --> 00:20:26.262
Oh, yes. I'm terrified.

395
00:20:26.304 --> 00:20:29.599
Nighty-Knight:
See? Megamind gets my darkness.


396
00:20:29.640 --> 00:20:32.477
- That's why he
left me in charge. -


397
00:20:32.518 --> 00:20:34.353
But that's not why we're here.

398
00:20:34.395 --> 00:20:36.689
We heard all about
your new job.


399
00:20:36.731 --> 00:20:38.274
You did?

400
00:20:38.316 --> 00:20:41.277
Nighty-Knight:
Yeah! You think we were gonna let that go


