00:20:41.319 --> 00:20:43.279
without paying you a visit?

402
00:20:43.321 --> 00:20:46.115
Let him have it, Behemoth!

403
00:20:49.160 --> 00:20:51.412
Guys!
Can't we just talk this--


404
00:20:51.454 --> 00:20:52.663
Ah!

405
00:20:53.664 --> 00:20:56.626
The Doom Syndicate: Congratulations!

406
00:20:56.667 --> 00:20:57.710
What?

407
00:20:57.752 --> 00:20:58.878
* For he's a horrible *

408
00:20:58.920 --> 00:21:00.088
* Evil fellow *

409
00:21:00.129 --> 00:21:02.131
* Which nobody can deny *

410
00:21:02.173 --> 00:21:03.716
* Because he's now
their evil overlord *


411
00:21:03.758 --> 00:21:07.053
* And they're likely to receive
an unusually cruel punishment *


