and wait for your signal,


414
00:21:16.229 --> 00:21:19.482
we had no idea
it was gonna be this!


415
00:21:19.524 --> 00:21:23.194
- Not even I could
conjure such an illusion. -


416
00:21:23.236 --> 00:21:26.364
Nighty-Knight:
It's dark, it's messed up,


417
00:21:26.406 --> 00:21:28.366
and I love it.

418
00:21:28.408 --> 00:21:29.534
Huh?

419
00:21:29.575 --> 00:21:32.829
Oh yeah, that's the stuff.

420
00:21:32.870 --> 00:21:36.499
You think
I'm pretending to be a hero.


421
00:21:36.541 --> 00:21:38.334
- Nighty-Knight: Huh?
- Oh.


422
00:21:38.376 --> 00:21:41.170
And you'd be right, of course!

423
00:21:41.212 --> 00:21:44.132
That was absolutely
my intention.


424
00:21:44.173 --> 00:21:47.802
There no way Megamind
could be real hero.


425
00:21:47.844 --> 00:21:50.471
That would be great
betrayal and cause


