00:22:18.416 --> 00:22:20.126
The Doom Syndicate!

437
00:22:20.168 --> 00:22:22.378
What's Roxanne Ritchi
doing here?!


438
00:22:22.420 --> 00:22:23.755
I assure you

439
00:22:23.796 --> 00:22:26.215
there's a completely evil
explanation for this.


440
00:22:27.675 --> 00:22:29.343
We're waiting.

441
00:22:29.385 --> 00:22:32.096
Yeah... so am I.

442
00:22:32.138 --> 00:22:35.850
Roxanne is here,
at this moment, right now,


443
00:22:35.892 --> 00:22:38.394
before us,
because she's agreed...


444
00:22:38.436 --> 00:22:39.645
Syndicate:
Yeah?


445
00:22:39.687 --> 00:22:43.191
- ...to be my evil bride.
- What?!


446
00:22:43.232 --> 00:22:45.026
They still think I'm evil

447
00:22:45.068 --> 00:22:46.778
and only pretending
to be a hero.


448
00:22:46.819 --> 00:22:49.030
- Play along!
- Is this true?


449
00:22:49.489 --> 00:22:52.909
More like too good to be true!

450
00:22:52.950 --> 00:22:55.161
